project: To learn how to play go to the instructions, if you are ready play!

To play this game you will get a theme, according to the theme is how you are going to be able to dress your model. You will style your model with hair, clothes, faces, accessories, and shoes. You will also have only thirty seconds to dress up your model, if you fail to complete your outfit and click the done button before the thirty seconds you will lose the game. If you finish press the done button before the timer runs out! You will press a randomized button and whichever button you choose will be how your model is rated for that game. Once you fully understand you can go back to the home page and then begin your game!
